               <p>Q. You did not name any note that did not appear on the file? - A. No; at the end of the day's work we sign the book.</p>
               <p>JOHN THEOBALDS sworn. - It was my duty to look at the cash-book, while my partner calls over the file, to see they correspond with the entries.</p>
